      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CALICO BLUFF (2) is a promising dog in the frame at nine of 24 starts including seven wins and was in the minors again latest (19.93) over 366m at this track. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Well placed here and can go close with a clear run. HARA'S JACKSON (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Jilliby Dymar (20.23) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to feature again. PAW FREDRICK (8) finished well back at Q Lakeside last time when a 4.5 lengths sixth (25.96) but scored three back at Geelong (26.01). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Bold showing expected. BUNDY BLAZE (1) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
